  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   1st Law of Thermodynamics
Formula: ΔU = Q - W
Note:    Energy conservation in thermodynamic systems

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Bayes Theorem
Formula: P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)
Note:    Updating probability based on new evidence

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Ohm's Law
Formula: V = IR
Note:    Voltage, current, resistance relationship in circuits

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Gravitational Force
Formula: F = Gm1m2/r²
Note:    Universal gravitation between all masses

Domain:  Medicine
